===VRRat plush===
[[File:VRRat_plush.jpg|thumb|Promotional image of the VRRat plush.]]
A VRRat plush<ref>[https://www.makeship.com/products/vrrat-plush VRRat Plush] on Makeship; retrieved November 29, 2024.</ref> was revealed as VRChat's fourth product campaign. The campaign ran from December 1st, 2024, to December 30, 2024.